OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780913124
OL,3,CLiverpool appoint Andoni Iraola as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FLiverpool have appointed Andoni Iraola
OL,7,Fas their new head coach.
OL,9,FThe 43-year-old is understood to have
OL,10,Fsigned a two-year contract after the
OL,11,Fsacking of Arne Slot last weekend.
OL,13,FIt came just a year after the Dutchman
OL,14,Fguided the Reds to the Premier League
OL,15,Ftitle.
OL,17,FThe club moved swiftly to tie up a
OL,18,Fdeal for Iraola, the former
OL,19,FBournemouth manager, who had already
OL,20,Fspoken to Crystal Palace, Bayer
OL,21,FLeverkusen and AC Milan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
