CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780913124
OL,3,CLiverpool appoint Andoni Iraola as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FHe arrives at the football club having
OL,7,Fhelped the Cherries to secure their
OL,8,Ffirst European campaign after
OL,9,Ffinishing sixth in the Premier League.
OL,11,FIraola says it's a 'special club':
OL,12,F"Really excited, really excited.
OL,13,FBecause obviously you know about
OL,14,FLiverpool, you know that it's a big
OL,15,Fclub, a massive club, one of the
OL,16,Fbiggest in the world," he told the
OL,17,Fclub's website.
OL,19,F"But feeling inside and understanding
OL,20,Fa little bit more of this club, I
OL,21,Falways thought it's a special club.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@VO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780913124
OL,3,CLiverpool appoint Andoni Iraola as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,F"You don't need a lot of things to get
OL,7,Fattracted by Liverpool. Liverpool is
OL,8,FLiverpool.
OL,10,F"But obviously the atmosphere, the
OL,11,Fsupporters, the club, the players, the
OL,12,Fchance for me to coach top-level
OL,13,Fplayers, the chance to fight for
OL,14,Ftitles.
OL,16,F"I think it cannot be more attractive
OL,17,Fthan this. It's difficult to find it.
OL,18,FSo, really excited to start."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOUzD@]O]
