PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780913124
OL,3,CLiverpool appoint Andoni Iraola as new
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FIraola flew into Merseyside on a
OL,7,Fprivate jet from San Sebastian in his
OL,8,Fhomeland, visiting the club's AXA
OL,9,Ftraining complex and Anfield before
OL,10,Freturning on the same plane late in
OL,11,Fthe afternoon.
OL,13,FIt is believed he wants to bring
OL,14,Fassistants Tommy Elphick and Shaun
OL,15,FCooper, analyst Tom Webber and fitness
OL,16,Fcoach Pablo de la Torre with him to
OL,17,Fthe club.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
